      <p class = "h4">Dark Rites</p>
      Dark Rites shall be construed as the rendering of service, supplication,
      or sacrifice to any malicious force or being which may cause potential
      harm to the Kingdom and its people; such as entering into bargains with
      Fae creatures.
      <p class = "h4">Enforcement of the Law</p>
      Within the jurisdiction of the town of Damar Keep it is the
      responsibility of the Militia and Constabulary oversight for the
      interpretation and enforcement of the laws of the Kingdom. As hands of
      the very Law itself, these entities are duty bound to both interpret and
      enact the laws in a manor of universal fairness. The Knights of the
      municipality and members of the Nobility shall have final say in the
      interpretation of any Law and the execution of the enforcement of these
      laws for especially heinous or cataclysmic crimes.
      <p class = "h4">Punishments for Common Crimes</p>
